{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the Lifetime ISA (LISA) maximum home purchase price",
        "additional_details": "The current maximum value of a property that can be purchased using a LISA as a first-time buyer is \u00a3450,000. This is not enough, especially due to house price increases in the last few years.\r\n \r\nIn many areas you are simply unable to buy a suitable home for \u00a3450,000. Especially due to the 10-20% increase in house prices over the last few years. The \u00a3450,000 home price limit should be increased, to at least \u00a3500,000.\r\n",
        "background": "I want the Government to increase the value of the maximum purchase price for a home when using the Lifetime ISA (LISA) scheme. ",
